To instruct students individually and in groups, I will use a variety of teaching methods to address different learning styles and needs. For whole-group instruction, I will deliver clear and engaging lectures, use visual aids, and facilitate class discussions to encourage participation and critical thinking. For small groups or individual students, I will provide targeted instruction, demonstrations, and hands-on activities to reinforce concepts and offer personalized support. Throughout, I will monitor understanding, ask questions, and adjust my teaching strategies to ensure all students are actively learning and progressing.
